benefits and downsides. Be sure you‚Äôre taking maximum benefit from it, avoiding
the negative effects as much as you can.¬†Pros ‚Ä¢	You can finally melt away that stubborn fat quickly by restricting calorie intake.‚Ä¢	Cutting down sugar and processed food prevents you from developing diabetes and cardiovascular diseases. It also helps shed extra pounds in a healthy way.‚Ä¢	Having daily vitamin supplements make you strong and you can easily meet your daily body requirements.‚Ä¢	Pro-ana diet plan encourages you to exercise daily. This is good for your general well being as well and helps you lose weight fastCons ‚Ä¢	After leaving the pro-ana diet, you‚Äôre expected to gain weight again.‚Ä¢	As calorie intake is way too less than the normal range which your body needs, you can experience health problems frequently.‚Ä¢	Having fewer meal times than normal may result in nutritional deficiencies and you can experience dizziness, fatigue, muscle weakness, and mental disorientation.‚Ä¢	If you‚Äôre following an extreme pro-ana diet plan, then you might experience starvation every day. This makes your body to function improperly as it considers this as a ‚Äúfight or flight‚Äù condition.Kick Out Stress From LifeThe research has shown the direct connection of
stress with weight gain. According to studies when we think a lot and in
stress, our body releases a large amount of cortisol hormone. This, in turn,
increases your appetite, slows down your metabolism and increase the craving
for the food. Thus, if you are depressed you want to eat more, that in return
cause an increase in weight. Therefore, if you want to reduce your weight, stop
stressing about your weight or any other stupid things. Remain tension free,
